{"tid":1759702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美心太子女伍淑清　入圍央視「感動中國年度人物」","createTime":"2019-11-27T21:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T00:19:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"89c13fd481c264c7be404716b0cb60edf652a96d","tid":1759702,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T21:38:32.000Z","msg":"反送中運動以來，美心集團創辦人伍沾德長女伍淑清多次發表撐警言論及批評示威者，觸發美心集團旗下食肆受到破壞。官媒央視近日舉行「感動中國2019年度人物評選」，伍淑清成為香港唯一候選人。<br />\n<br />\n央視今年有 21 個候選人供網民投票，目前伍淑清已得票超過35萬，僅次於四川森林消防員排名第二位。央視在簡介中形容，伍淑清一家人「愛國愛港」，回歸後致力於香港和內地的交流合作，建立教育基金，積極增進香港青年對中華歷史和文化的認識。<br />\n<br />\n央視讚揚伍淑清在修例風波發生以來，「嚴辭阻止亂港分子發起的學生罷課，成為亂港分子的眼中釘、肉中刺，他們放言要聲討、抵制伍淑清及美心集團」，並指她在 9 月現身日內瓦聯合國人權理事會例會，「向世界說出真實的香港」。<br />\n<br />\n伍淑清曾經在瑞士日內瓦聯合國人權理事會例會上稱發表撐警言論，指修例初衷「用心良苦」被示威者「騎劫」，「世界各地的警察均有使用催淚彈及橡膠子彈，並非香港獨有」。<br />\n<br />\n她日前接受央視訪問，提到早前出席聯合國人權理事會，是以民間的方式向國際解釋香港現況，形容香港一般人「有苦說不出口」，至於由其家族創辦的美心集團，因而受到影響，她認為是無可避免。美心 1972 年引入怡和系旗下置地公司為股東，現時怡和系的牛奶國際持有 50% 美心股權，另一半由伍氏家族擁有。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/2019111312072355830_nYONR_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F2019111312072355830_nYONR_1200x0.png&h=f0e9e985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E4%BC%8D%E6%B7%91%E6%B8%85-%E5%85%A5%E5%9C%8D%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96-%E6%84%9F%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BC%258D%25E6%25B7%2591%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%25A9%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=b5d9e221\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BC%258D%25E6%25B7%2591%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%25A9%2F&h=a38166b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E4%BC%8D%E6%B7%91%E6%B8%85-%E5%85%A5%E5%9C%8D%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96-%E6%84%9F%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9/</a>"},{"pid":"3e9daf21dd5d4dd5e19df13900c798da73c887fb","tid":1759702,"uid":149607,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T21:39:39.000Z","msg":"中华人民共和国<br />\n真係一個好嘔心既國家"},{"pid":"a9c8aa17ab2fd21c9c7bb06c72b7687baf5e8fbf","tid":1759702,"uid":302905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T21:41:09.000Z","msg":"攞啲感嘅名頭，真係釘上恥辱柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb10c4d0042fbce0bfd87e59c0ce345c2f89e34","tid":1759702,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T21:41:17.000Z","msg":"原來中國人有得投票架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04be140c2c9d038fafb8694eab8d3d0b78519693","tid":1759702,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T21:48:51.000Z","msg":"同以前釘十字架示眾既FEEL"},{"pid":"4bc4aa1eb0cadb84c292fcf8ec80de26873267ab","tid":1759702,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T22:03:42.000Z","msg":"無時無刻提醒香港人美心集團是賤人企業"},{"pid":"b05ed1ad2dd379862a9aeeeaabf8c22c8d2aabb2","tid":1759702,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T22:07:32.000Z","msg":"條廢老睇黎好憎美心既當權者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5bd30ca93b6a8d746570bd8ec3293659a29eb6","tid":1759702,"uid":141151,"l